    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "It's temporary, the idea is to remove timestamps from messages entirely and [have them show up on tap or gesture only.](https://github.com/status-im/status-react/issues/10734) So while I agree it's imperfect, I think it's something we can live with. For a quick fix, I'd hide the duration of the audio message since it's really not that important: the audio is already downloaded, if you feel like it's too long then you can pause it, I doubt anyone cares if it's 10 seconds or 30.",
